{"tid":2327478,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"湯告魯斯錄音流出 爆粗狂鬧工作人員違反社交距離","createTime":"2020-12-16T05:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T14:59:09.000Z","uid":11676,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a622439066dd6881395c2b00b92353d0dc9d429","tid":2327478,"uid":11676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise）主演之招牌動作系列《職業特工隊7》（Mission: Impossible 7），因為武漢肺炎早前已停工5個月。到8月又因為電單車意外爆炸令拍攝停工，經過重重波折才能復拍。今日就有巨星的錄音流出，內容為他見到兩名工作人員社交距離不足而震怒，更爆粗鬧人。<br />\n<br />\n由於兩名工作人員站得太近去看電腦的螢光幕，令湯告魯斯扯火，他表示：「我們是有黃金般的規則，他們能重回荷李活拍戲是因為我們，他們都信任我們在做的事。我們創造了過千份工作，你們這些X街，我不要再見到！永不！」他又表示晚晚都與電影公司、保險公司、監製通話確保拍攝進度，難怪大壓力：「我每晚都是這樣睡覺，與這X街行業！如果你不做好，你就被炒，我們不會再停止拍攝這部戲！你明白嗎？如果我再見到，你就唔X見人。」對拍攝進度與抗疫問題非常緊張。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201216/5VKAZKXXGBDZ7IUKK3GYKCAW5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201216%2F5VKAZKXXGBDZ7IUKK3GYKCAW5M%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=90ddcd4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201216%2F5VKAZKXXGBDZ7IUKK3GYKCAW5M%2F&h=f96057a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201216/5VKAZKXXGBDZ7IUKK3GYKCAW5M/</a>"},{"pid":"2dd2051387322ff0ddb8eede0a5c378ecd42b90e","tid":2327478,"uid":11676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=6GLl0C2R_O0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6GLl0C2R_O0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=2d0669c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=6GLl0C2R_O0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"0ac1832504e31611511ede448062aa4b075d89a2","tid":2327478,"uid":148749,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"佢中文咁好架咩"},{"pid":"7b0ad75129a81b16